name: Bubble Popper (Anciny)
description:
The ocean is filled with bubbles and you’ve got an urge to pop them! Can you beat the high score in this endless ocean shooter?

Game Jam Theme: Bubbles

Game Jam Limitation: You are your own ammo

Music: Sunny by https://www.bensound.com/

Sound: dustyroom.com

Background Sprites: https://olgas-lab.itch.io/underwater-background

Created: 9-11th of July for the Mini Jam 84: Bubbles
